\frac{2x+7}{\sqrt{x^2+2x-1}}=\frac{x(2+\frac{7}{x})}{\sqrt{x^2(1+\frac{2}{x}-\frac{1}{x^2})}}=\frac{x(2+\frac{7}{x})}{(\left | x \right |)\sqrt{1+\frac{2}{x}-\frac{1}{x^2}}}
\left | x \right |=-x
